Package: sibyldata
Type: Package
Title: SIBYL Data Pipeline
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Wraps readabs, readrba, fredr, and the OECD package into a single
    update_data() function that returns tidy panels with vintage tracking,
    cached locally as parquet via arrow. Provides the series-ID -> MARTIN
    variable map that lets sibyldata feed packages/martin.
